going in pen, baby.[chuckles] Oh.

00:15.450 --> 00:18.061
I love it when you get all
confident during word games.

00:18.105 --> 00:19.628
Thank you.

00:19.671 --> 00:23.023
Uh, the 2018 NBA Rookie of
the Year is none other than...

00:23.066 --> 00:24.850
he's my favorite player...

00:24.894 --> 00:26.461
I want to name my
child after him...

00:26.504 --> 00:28.898
