feeling when you know

01:13.247 --> 01:14.944
you're in love right away?Oh, totally.

01:14.987 --> 01:16.076
Like, uh, when we first started

01:16.119 --> 01:17.251
mixing M&M's
in with our popcorn.

01:17.294 --> 01:21.559
[chuckles] So, who's
the lucky lady?

01:21.603 --> 01:23.083
Vanessa Cole.

01:23.126 --> 01:24.867
That country singer who sings
"That Dog Ain't Right."

01:24.910 --> 01:26.390
Oh, we love that song, right?CLAIRE: Yeah.

01:26.434 --> 01:30.133
♪ Oh, he'll chew your stuff
and bark all night ♪

01:30.177 --> 01:33.528
♪ He'll bite your ankles
with all his might ♪

01:33.571 --> 01:35.356
♪ Yes, it's plain to see

01:35.399 --> 01:38.098
BOTH:
♪ That dog ain't right.

01:38.141 --> 01:40.274
[both laugh]

01:42.928 --> 01:47.063
So, you're dating Vanessa.

01:47.107 --> 01:48.543
Well, before she goes
on her fall tour,

01:48.586 --> 01:50.197
I want to surprise her
with a big, romantic gesture,

01:50.240 --> 01:51.981
but I'm kind of sick
of my go-to moves.

01:52.024 --> 01:53.461
You know, like renting out
Dodger's Stadium

01:53.504 --> 01:55.071
to watch Field of Dreams...Right.

01:55.115 --> 01:57.247
...or eating a 12-course meal
at the Vatican.
Of course.

01:57.291 --> 01:59.641
How did you pull that off?

01:59.684 --> 02:00.903
Oh, I know the owner.

02:00.946 --> 02:02.948
God?

02:02.992 --> 02:05.255
So, I was thinking,

02:05.299 --> 02:08.171
you guys have been together
for half my life...

02:08.215 --> 02:11.522
Feels like a hurtful
way to keep time.
No.

02:11.566 --> 02:14.090
What big, romantic moves
have you done over the years?

02:14.134 --> 02:16.048
Oh. [laughs]
Oh. [laughs]

02:16.092 --> 02:17.441
Don't even get us...Don't get us started.

02:17.485 --> 02:19.748
Right?
Because once we start,
we ain't stopping.

02:19.791 --> 02:21.532
Yeah. There's so many,
it's like, um...

02:21.576 --> 02:23.230
