by filling up my car with gas.Mm-hmm.

02:39.681 --> 02:41.509
'Cause everyone knows that
the way to a woman's heart

02:41.552 --> 02:44.164
is through her gas tank.

02:45.252 --> 02:47.993
That's not a euphemism.

02:48.037 --> 02:49.212
JAKE:
Oh, I know.

02:49.256 --> 02:51.214
Um, like, uh, Claire,
she always leaves me

02:51.258 --> 02:53.173
cute, little, sexy notes

02:53.216 --> 02:56.001
like this one I found
in my, uh, briefcase today.

02:56.045 --> 02:58.047
[chuckles]

02:58.090 --> 03:01.006
[sexy voice]:
"Jake, please buy lightbulbs."

03:03.922 --> 03:06.403
I mean, I can't be the only one
who's getting goose bumps. Huh?

03:07.665 --> 03:09.276
Look at that. [chuckles]

03:09.319 --> 03:11.408
You know what? We're past
all that stuff. You know?

03:11.452 --> 03:13.454
