prescription toothpaste.Aw, yeah.

03:16.544 --> 03:18.285
That's right, baby.

03:18.328 --> 03:21.201
[inhales]

03:21.244 --> 03:23.290
[coughs]

03:25.248 --> 03:26.858
It's working.

03:26.902 --> 03:29.383
It's working and,
uh, so are we.

03:31.385 --> 03:32.342
All right, well, let me know

03:32.386 --> 03:33.735
if you think of anything.

03:33.778 --> 03:36.259
All right.[laughs]

03:36.303 --> 03:38.392
You know, babe, I didn't
want to embarrass you
in front of Cooper,

03:38.435 --> 03:40.785
but that toothpaste
is not working.

03:43.919 --> 03:46.008
♪ Imagine me and you

03:46.051 --> 03:48.358
♪ I do

03:48.402 --> 03:50.665
♪ I think about you
day and night ♪

03:50.708 --> 03:52.754
♪ It's only right

03:52.797 --> 03:56.453
♪ So happy together

03:56.497 --> 03:57.802
♪ Ba-ba-ba-ba

03:57.846 --> 04:02.981
♪ Ba-ba-ba-ba-ba-ba-ba.

04:09.336 --> 04:10.728
I'd like
to propose a toast.

04:10.772 --> 04:12.730
Yay.

04:12.774 --> 04:14.602
To my beautiful wife

04:14.645 --> 04:16.952
who makes me excited
to wake up every day.
Aw.

04:16.995 --> 04:18.301
Happy birthday, baby.

04:18.345 --> 04:20.172
Ah, happy birthday.

04:20.216 --> 04:22.305
Thank you.
Thank you.
Super sweet.

04:22.349 --> 04:24.742
Cooper says happy
birthday, as well.

04:24.786 --> 04:26.570
He'd be here,
but he rented out SeaWorld

04:26.614 --> 04:28.746
