we don't do those things?

04:48.810 --> 04:49.985
Of course it is.

04:50.028 --> 04:51.595
That big, showy stuff
is for new couples

04:51.639 --> 04:53.336
who don't know
what true love is.

04:53.380 --> 04:54.772
GERALD:
I don't know.

04:54.816 --> 04:55.773
I think every
once in a while

04:55.817 --> 04:57.558
a big move can be nice.

04:57.601 --> 04:59.603
Trust me, honey, a small,
quiet dinner with my family,

04:59.647 --> 05:00.952
that's all I need.

05:00.996 --> 05:03.433
