take your breath away.

06:31.303 --> 06:33.871
Definitely. You know,
it's like those fake candles

06:33.915 --> 06:35.830
that they have
at The Cheesecake Factory.

06:35.873 --> 06:38.615
Consistent, yet electric.
Yep.

06:40.661 --> 06:42.793
[lisping]: Yeah.
You know, I just...

06:42.837 --> 06:44.665
I just want to make sure
we're still passionate.

06:44.708 --> 06:46.057
You know?

06:46.101 --> 06:48.103
[lisping]: Sweetie,
we are so passionate.

06:48.146 --> 06:50.279
It's all good.

06:50.322 --> 06:54.414
Oh, wait, stop, babe.
We forgot to kiss.
[sighs]

06:54.457 --> 06:56.807
Well, let's just have
a makeup kiss at breakfast.

06:56.851 --> 07:01.725
Okay? Mm. Good night.

07:01.769 --> 07:03.684
Sleep tight, sweetie.

07:03.727 --> 07:04.946
Okay.

07:12.867 --> 07:15.783
I have been married to Claire
for four years now,

07:15.826 --> 07:17.262
and I just want
to do something big

07:17.306 --> 07:18.742
to remind her
how much I love her.

07:18.786 --> 07:21.179
So what's,
like, a cool,

07:21.223 --> 07:24.400
over-the-top romantic move
I could do?

07:24.444 --> 07:27.316
Do you want the name
of my stadium guy?

07:29.623 --> 07:31.581
I can't rent out Dodger Stadium.

07:31.625 --> 07:34.584
Are you not a baseball fan?

07:34.628 --> 07:36.499
Eh...

07:36.543 --> 07:39.763
Yeah, dude, that's the only
speed bump in that plan.

07:41.243 --> 07:43.593
What about a private flight
to Fiji?
All right.

07:43.637 --> 07:44.986
Listen, you are at a Bentley,

07:45.029 --> 07:48.163
I'm-a need you
at a bus pass, okay?

07:49.773 --> 07:52.733
What is the most affordable
grand gesture you've done?

07:52.776 --> 07:55.518
Well, I got my last girlfriend's
name tattooed on my body.

07:55.562 --> 07:56.998
Oh, Claire loves tattoos!

07:57.041 --> 07:59.522
Ah, but that might only be
when they're on The Rock.

07:59.566 --> 08:00.871
Dwayne is such a sweet guy.

08:00.915 --> 08:02.177
Why don't I text him

08:02.220 --> 08:06.224
to see if he can take Claire
on a picnic.
No!

08:06.268 --> 08:07.835
No!

08:09.880 --> 08:13.188
Sorry. No. I...

08:13.231 --> 08:15.320
I don't want that.

08:15.364 --> 08:18.280
But that tattoo idea
is perfect, you know.

08:18.323 --> 08:20.804
It-It's sexy,
it's permanent, you know.

08:20.848 --> 08:22.371
Plus, Claire would
never see it coming

08:22.414 --> 08:24.286
because she knows I'm afraid
of needles. [laughs]

08:27.115 --> 08:30.901
[needles buzzing]Ahh!

08:30.945 --> 08:34.078
Hey, uh, what are we talking
on the pain scale here, huh?

08:34.122 --> 08:35.297
It's more of a tickle.

08:35.340 --> 08:38.343
[screaming]

08:38.387 --> 08:40.128
Ooh, tickly.

08:40.998 --> 08:41.999
So, Jake, where'd you like

08:42.043 --> 08:44.741
to get your tattoo today?

08:44.785 --> 08:46.482
Uh, probably a cleaner room,
that'd be nice,

08:46.526 --> 08:49.311
uh, maybe somewhere
with a little more privacy.

08:50.138 --> 08:51.574
He means where on your body.

08:51.618 --> 08:52.923
Oh.

08:52.967 --> 08:56.100
Well, as Captain Hook says
with his treasure maps,

08:56.144 --> 08:57.841
"Flex marks
the spot."

08:57.885 --> 08:58.973
Huh?

08:59.016 --> 09:00.975
He wants it on his shoulder.

09:01.018 --> 09:02.977
Jake, are you absolutely sure
about this?

09:03.020 --> 09:04.892
Yeah, I am,
I'm-I'm sure.

09:04.935 --> 09:06.850
Uh, you know, I'm-I'm
crazy about Claire.

09:06.894 --> 09:08.809
I want to do something
crazy for her,

09:08.852 --> 09:11.289
something big,
something romantic, you know?

09:11.333 --> 09:12.682
Got it.

09:12.726 --> 09:16.643
I can make your junk
look like a dragon.

09:16.686 --> 09:20.385
Uh, great brainstorming sesh,
buddy, that's-that's nice,

09:20.429 --> 09:22.605
but, um, I was thinking
something a little less scary

09:22.649 --> 09:24.868
and a little more, uh, swirly.

09:24.912 --> 09:26.348
You're the boss.

09:26.391 --> 09:28.916
Okay, just raise
your finger

09:28.959 --> 09:31.092
if you need me to stop
for any reason.

09:31.135 --> 09:33.181
[chuckles] The only finger
I'll be raising is my thumb

09:33.224 --> 09:35.096
because hell yeah, dude.

09:35.139 --> 09:38.926
[needle buzzing][screaming]

09:38.969 --> 09:40.710
Ha-ha!

09:40.754 --> 09:43.713
It tickles!
You were right!

09:43.757 --> 09:46.760
It tickles so bad!

09:57.292 --> 09:58.902
Oh, Jake, guess what,

09:58.946 --> 10:01.209
there was a crossword
clue about the IRS.

10:01.252 --> 10:03.037
It was ten letters,
started with a "C."

10:03.080 --> 10:05.605
Compulsory.

10:09.783 --> 10:11.132
Where have you been?

10:11.175 --> 10:13.656
Well, I had lunch with Coop-dog,

10:13.700 --> 10:15.353
went and picked up
your lightbulbs.

10:15.397 --> 10:16.920
Oh.

10:16.964 --> 10:19.401
Oh, and I, uh,
slammed a little body art.

10:19.444 --> 10:21.055
Wait, what?

10:21.098 --> 10:24.928
Oh, you're talking about
my "champ stamp"?

10:24.972 --> 10:28.149
Jake, is that a freaking tattoo?
Oh, my God, well, let me see it.

10:28.192 --> 10:32.196
Easy, easy.
No touching the dancers.

10:33.807 --> 10:36.200
He said I'm not supposed to take
the bandages off yet, but, uh,

10:36.244 --> 10:41.075
tat-rats like us don't
play by the rules, so...

10:41.118 --> 10:44.165
[muttering]

10:45.949 --> 10:47.951
Ready?
Here, ready?

10:49.083 --> 10:52.129
Ah, just peel that...

10:52.173 --> 10:54.523
[moans]

11:03.488 --> 11:05.839
Woo.
[laughs]

11:05.882 --> 11:10.539
Jake, aw!

11:10.582 --> 11:13.150
You got my name
tattooed on your arm.

11:13.194 --> 11:14.674
Yup.

11:14.717 --> 11:16.371
Did it hurt?

11:16.414 --> 11:19.679
I screamed so much they made me
put my own socks in my mouth.

11:19.722 --> 11:23.117
Oh, my God, well, this is
the most romantic thing ever.

11:26.337 --> 11:29.384
But...
But what?

11:29.427 --> 11:30.994
Nothing. It's just...

11:31.038 --> 11:34.084
I don't know, this is so sweet,
and it just makes me feel bad

11:34.128 --> 11:36.173
'cause I've never done anything
big like this for you.

11:36.217 --> 11:40.700
Sea bass,
don't you dare.

11:43.790 --> 11:46.096
I may be painted,

11:46.140 --> 11:49.099
but you're the masterpiece
around here, okay?

11:49.143 --> 11:52.537
[laughs] Okay. Ah...

11:52.581 --> 11:55.323
You know, I've never hooked up
with a tattoo guy before.

11:55.366 --> 11:58.456
Oh, well, all that's
about to change because, uh,

11:58.500 --> 12:00.197
as they say
in Space Jam,

12:00.241 --> 12:04.201
"Y'all ready for this?"

12:06.073 --> 12:08.075
Well, I'm excited
to help, Claire,

12:08.118 --> 12:09.641
but just because Jake
did something over the top

12:09.685 --> 12:11.121
doesn't mean
you have to as well.

12:11.165 --> 12:14.951
Mm, you have no idea
how marriage works, do you?

12:16.910 --> 12:18.694
I just felt so special
when I saw his tattoo,

12:18.738 --> 12:20.914
I want to make sure that Jake
feels the same way.

12:20.957 --> 12:23.307
Okay, well, I usually start
with something they like

12:23.351 --> 12:25.788
and then build from it.
So what's Jake into?

12:25.832 --> 12:28.835
Um, well, he is really into

12:28.878 --> 12:32.012
food, sleeping, playing ball...

12:32.055 --> 12:36.625
Oh, my God, I married
a Golden Retriever.

12:39.106 --> 12:41.064
You, uh, you mentioned food,

12:41.108 --> 12:43.588
would, uh, would Jake like to
cook a meal with Gordon Ramsey?

12:43.632 --> 12:45.068
If you pay extra

12:45.112 --> 12:46.896
he yells at you until you feel
like absolute garbage,

12:46.940 --> 12:48.158
it's pretty great.

12:48.202 --> 12:51.422
Uh, well, he's-he's
not into gourmet food.

12:51.466 --> 12:55.818
Okay, um, what about a sparring
session with Conor McGregor?

12:55.862 --> 12:59.256
