against right now.

13:04.261 --> 13:06.742
Okay, give me that thing.
I need to see your contacts.

13:08.918 --> 13:10.702
Oh, my God, you're friends
with The Rock?

13:10.746 --> 13:11.703
[laughs]

13:11.747 --> 13:12.879
Oh, my God...

13:12.922 --> 13:14.445
No!

13:18.188 --> 13:20.408
No. No, um,

13:20.451 --> 13:23.541
yeah, I don't think
Jake would like that.

13:27.589 --> 13:31.158
[chuckles]

13:31.201 --> 13:34.378
Whoa, man,
nice ink, bro.

13:34.422 --> 13:35.902
It's killer.
I'm a bit of a

13:35.945 --> 13:38.861
squid myself.

13:38.905 --> 13:40.645
Thinking about getting
a whole sleeve.

13:40.689 --> 13:41.908
